The '''Cavrilhu Pirates''' were a group of [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] based in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]].

==History==
{{Quote|Opportunists. Carrion birds who follow warriors and pick the battlefields clean. They want a quick fight, if they must fight at all.|Jagged Fel to Shawnkyr Nuruodo|<ref name="RSBF">{{GamerCite|7|Red Sky, Blue Flame}}</ref>}}
Led by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Zothip]] from aboard the ''[[Void Cutter]]'', the pirates operated from a number of hidden bases, like [[Cavrilhu's Kauron base|their facility]] in the [[Kauron]] [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] [[Asteroid field/Legends|belt]].

During the [[Thrawn campaign]], [[Niles Ferrier]] managed to steal three [[IPV-1 System Patrol Craft]] in the [[Amorris system/Legends|Amorris system]] from them in order to sell the ships to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]].<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref><ref name="DFR">''[[Dark Force Rising]]''</ref>

In the period preceding [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]], Zothip began providing [[Preybird-class starfighter|''Preybird''-class starfighters]] to the [[Imperial Remnant]] through a deal with [[Graemon|Lord Graemon]] and [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Vilim Disra]]. The deal went sour when forces loyal to [[Fleet Admiral/Legends|Fleet Admiral]] [[Gilad Pellaeon/Legends|Gilad Pellaeon]] discovered that they were being purchased from the pirates, rather than [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]].

[[File:Clawcraft_Chiss.jpg|thumb|right|200px|[[Jagged Fel]] fighting a Cavrilhu [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing]] in the [[Rata Nebula/Legends|Rata Nebula]].]]

After Disra canceled the deal, Zothip and several others headed to confront Disra on [[Bastion/Legends|Bastion]]. Zothip met his end shortly before the [[Pellaeon–Gavrisom Treaty]] was signed, when one of his [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenants]], a pirate named [[Control (individual)|Control]], engineered a confrontation between Zothip and Disra. Zothip was killed by the [[Mistryl Shadow Guard]] [[Karoly D'ulin]], and Control was left to take over the Cavrilhu Pirates. In 19 ABY, [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] managed to [[Mission to the Kauron asteroid field|infiltrate]] their base in the Kauron asteroid belt but was captured and survived only due to the timely arrival of [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]].

After Luke Skywalker and Mara Jade escaped from their base, the Cavrilhu Pirates looked for the two [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and eventually found their trace in the [[Nirauan system/Legends|Nirauan system]]. When the pirates arrived on [[Nirauan/Legends|Nirauan]], the Jedi were already gone but they found the [[Hand of Thrawn]]. Due to the destruction of their defenses by the Jedi, the personnel of the base were forced to evacuate and the pirates captured the base.<ref name="RSBF" />

